BPAC_ON          |  3 & 21 | Bright pixels atmospheric correction activated (water)
HIGH_GLINT       |  2 & 21 | High (uncorrected) glint (water)
TOAVI_INVAL_REC  |  2 & 23 | Invalid rectification (land)
LOW_SUN          |  1      | Sun low above horizon (or conversely high sun zenith angle)
WHITE_SCATTERER  |  0 & 21 | Presence of white scatterer in water
